			<div class="b2mif">
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Java, Bedrock</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Plugins</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">24/7</span>
			</div>
			<a href="/minecraft" class="b2mia">More Info <i class="fi fi-rr-arrow-right"></i></a>
		</div>
		<div class="banner2-menu-item animate-up">
			<img src="discord2.png" class="card-icon">
			<div class="b2mih">
				<span>DISCORD</span>
				<p>Premium</p>
			</div>
			<span class="b2mis">High Quality Discord Bot hosting Servers with great Functionality and support.</span>
			<div class="b2mif">
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">NodeJS</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Performance</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">24/7</span>
			</div>
			<a href="/discordbot" class="b2mia">More Info <i class="fi fi-rr-arrow-right"></i></a>
		</div>
		<div class="banner2-menu-item b2miun animate-up">
			<img src="BeamNG.png" class="card-icon">
			<div class="b2mih">
				<span>BEAMMP</span>
				<p>Premium</p>
			</div>
			<span class="b2mis">High Quality BeamMp(BeamNG) Servers with great Performance and support.</span>
			<div class="b2mif">
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Cheap</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Mods Support(Not yet)</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">24/7</span>
			</div>
			<a class="b2mia">Coming Soon <i class="fi fi-rr-cross"></i></a>
		</div>
		<div class="banner2-menu-item b2miun animate-up">
			<img src="palworld.jpg" class="card-icon">
			<div class="b2mih">
				<span>PALWORLD</span>
				<p>Premium</p>
			</div>
			<span class="b2mis">High Quality Palworld Servers with great customization and support.</span>
			<div class="b2mif">
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Cheap</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">Smooth Gameplay</span>
				<span><img src="tickmark.svg">24/7</span>
			</div>
			<a class="b2mia">Coming Soon <i class="fi fi-rr-cross"></i></a>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="vr"></div>
<div class="banner3">
	<span class="banner3-quote1 animate-up" id="services">Easy to use</span>
	<span class="banner3-title1 animate-up">See our panel</span>
	<span class="banner3-subtitle1 animate-up">Explore the standout capabilities that make our platform the ideal solution for what you need.</span>
	<div class="banner3-seg">
		<div class="banner3-seg1 animate-up">
			<span class="banner3-seg1-title"></span>
			<div class="banner3-seg1-bar"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="banner3-seg2 animate-up">
			<img id="banner3-seg2-img">
		</div>
	</div>
	<script>
			window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
			const panels = [
				{ title: "DASHBOARD", img: "/panel1.png" },
				{ title: "CONSOLE", img: "/panel2.png" },
				{ title: "FILE MANAGER", img: "/panel3.png" }
			];

			let index = 0;

			const bar = document.querySelector('.banner3-seg1-bar');
			const img = document.querySelector('#banner3-seg2-img');
			const title = document.querySelector('.banner3-seg1-title');

			// ðŸ”¹ set FIRST state immediately
			if (img) img.src = panels[0].img;
			if (title) title.innerHTML = panels[0].title;
			bar?.classList.add('active');

			// ðŸ” cycle every 5 seconds
			setInterval(() => {
				index = (index + 1) % panels.length;

				if (img) img.src = panels[index].img;
				if (title) title.innerHTML = panels[index].title;

				// restart animation cleanly
				bar?.classList.remove('active');
				void bar?.offsetWidth; // force reflow
				bar?.classList.add('active');

			}, 5000);
			});
		</script>
</div>
<div class="vr"></div>
<div class="banner4">
        <span class="b4t animate-up">Why NodeForge?</span>
        <span class="b4s animate-up">We, at NodeForge, are here to give you the best experience.</span>
        <div class="b4-cards">
            <div class="b4-card animate-up">
                <span class="b4c-icon"><i class="fi fi-rr-user"></i></span>
                <span class="b4c-title">Personalized</span>
                <span class="b4c-subtitle">We tailor our services to meet your specific needs, ensuring a customized experience that fits your requirements.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="b4-card animate-up">
                <span class="b4c-icon"><i class="fi fi-rr-diamond"></i></span>
                <span class="b4c-title">Quality</span>
                <span class="b4c-subtitle">We deliver high-quality services that exceed expectations and provide a seamless experience.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="b4-card animate-up">
                <span class="b4c-icon"><i class="fi fi-rr-heart"></i></span>
                <span class="b4c-title">Dedicated</span>
                <span class="b4c-subtitle">We provide dedicated support and attention to ensure your satisfaction and success.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="b4-card animate-up">
                <span class="b4c-icon"><i class="fi fi-rr-user-headset"></i></span>
                <span class="b4c-title">Support</span>
                <span class="b4c-subtitle">We offer 24/7 support to assist you with any issues or questions you may have.</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
<div class="vr"></div>
<div class="banner5">
	<span class="b5t animate-up">Locations available</span>
    <span class="b5s animate-up">Locations our servers are available in.</span>
	<div class="b5-seg">
		<div class="b5-seg1">
			<div id="b5seg1finland"><img src="/Finland.svg">FINLAND</div>
			<div id="b5seg1india"><img src="/India.png">INDIA</div>
		</div>
		<div class="b5-seg2">
			<img src="/dotted-world-map.png">
			<div id="b5seg2finland"></div>
			<div id="b5seg2india"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</Layout>
